      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for throughout its ownership. Mechanically, it is very sound, shifting smoothly and handling well on both city streets and highways. The interior is clean with only minor signs of use, and all electronic features are fully functional. While the exterior looks great overall, there are a few minor surface scratches and small stone chips consistent with regular driving. It serves as a dependable and comfortable car for anyone looking for a quality pre-owned vehicle that needs no immediate repairs.",
