      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute gem. It is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s completely spotless inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new and ready for its next adventure, you\u2019ve found it! I'm happy to answer any questions you have, so just give me a shout!",
