    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, presented in breathtaking, showroom-fresh condition. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with absolutely zero rock chips or imperfections, while the interior remains pristine\u2014the premium leather still retains its original factory scent and supple texture with no visible wear. Mechanically, it is flawless; every service has been performed ahead of schedule at certified dealerships, and the undercarriage is as clean as the body. Garage-kept under a soft cover its entire life and never driven in inclement weather, this car offers a rare opportunity for a discerning collector to own a piece of automotive perfection that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
